node.title: London is going to be special...📽: @tairosslewis #VIP @johnnydangandco

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BT 🕊 on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.
Photo by BT 🕊 on August 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, wrist watch and indoor.

node.text: Damn, what if I would have quit back in 2018 when I lost damn near all of my income? 🥲Or maybe even all the other times things weren’t going the way I wanted them to. It’s definitely happened a lot more times than none .... I had so many opportunities and reasons to quit, but I realized I had all the opportunities and reasons in the world to keep going! I cried then to smile later. Memphis tomorrow!  #itllallmakesense

node.text: We did 5 cities in 5 days. Packed out every room so I decided to lightly celebrate the work in the club last night 🤷🏾‍♂️ #TJDAY #itllallmakesense

node.text: My portfolio is giving what it needs to give right now, the business is giving what it needs to give .... Stocks, cryptos, real estate they’re all giving. I really don’t feel like I brag enough. New Orleans Tomorrow  #itllallmakesense

node.text: The world making a turn again. We all see it. It’s no secret. I usually tell people to stay in their own lane......But honestly for the sake of time, you may need to be in ours. Houston next ✈️ #itllallmakesense
